1
00:00:02,127 --> 00:00:03,628
Damn Rolos.

2
00:00:05,672 --> 00:00:07,132
- Hey, you're back.
- Hey.

3
00:00:07,173 --> 00:00:08,508
How was your conference?

4
00:00:08,591 --> 00:00:10,677
It was terrible, I fought with..

5
00:00:10,719 --> 00:00:13,013
...my colleagues,
you know, the entire time.

6
00:00:13,096 --> 00:00:15,849
Are you kidding with this?

7
00:00:15,890 --> 00:00:17,767
Uh, so your weekend
was a total bust?

8
00:00:17,851 --> 00:00:19,436
Uh, no, I got
to see Donald Trump

9
00:00:19,519 --> 00:00:21,563
waiting for an elevator.

10
00:00:23,273 --> 00:00:24,858
- Hi.
- Hey, you're back too.

11
00:00:24,941 --> 00:00:27,068
Yeah, um, Chandler,
can I talk to you

12
00:00:27,152 --> 00:00:28,194
outside for just a second?

13
00:00:28,236 --> 00:00:29,362
Hey, how was your chef thing?

14
00:00:29,446 --> 00:00:31,489
Uh, it was awful.

15
00:00:31,531 --> 00:00:34,034
Guess some people just don't
appreciate really good food.

16
00:00:34,117 --> 00:00:36,536
Well, maybe it was the kind of
food that tasted good at first

17
00:00:36,619 --> 00:00:39,706
but then...made everybody
vomit and have diarrhea.

18
00:00:42,792 --> 00:00:43,918
Chandler?

19
00:00:44,002 --> 00:00:45,295
[imitating Monica]
Monica?

20
00:00:46,171 --> 00:00:47,797
Hey.

21
00:00:47,839 --> 00:00:49,883
Hey, Mr. Bing.

22
00:00:49,966 --> 00:00:52,302
That, uh, hotel
you stayed at called.

23
00:00:53,887 --> 00:00:56,890
Said someone left
an eyelash curler in your room.

24
00:00:59,434 --> 00:01:01,352
Yes, that was mine.

25
00:01:02,896 --> 00:01:04,355
'Cause I figured you
hooked up with some girl

26
00:01:04,439 --> 00:01:06,107
and she left it there.

27
00:01:06,191 --> 00:01:09,444
Yes, that would
have made more sense.

28
00:01:09,527 --> 00:01:13,490
You know, I-I don't even feel
like I know you anymore, man.

29
00:01:13,531 --> 00:01:14,783
Alright, uh..

30
00:01:14,866 --> 00:01:16,326
Look, I'm just
gonna ask you this

31
00:01:16,367 --> 00:01:18,870
one time, alright? And whatever
you say, I'll believe you.

32
00:01:21,039 --> 00:01:23,958
Were you...or were you not..

33
00:01:24,042 --> 00:01:25,752
...on a gay cruise?

34
00:01:27,045 --> 00:01:27,629
[instrumental music]

35
00:01:27,629 --> 00:01:28,671
- Hey.
- Hey.

36
00:01:28,755 --> 00:01:30,423
- Hey.
- Oh, hey, Monica.

37
00:01:30,465 --> 00:01:32,383
I heard you saw Donald Trump
at your convention.

38
00:01:32,425 --> 00:01:34,844
Yeah. Saw him waiting
for an elevator.

39
00:01:38,139 --> 00:01:39,599
Hey, Rach, can I borrow
your eyelash curler?

40
00:01:39,682 --> 00:01:42,018
- I think I lost mine.
- Yeah, it's in the bathroom.

41
00:01:47,565 --> 00:01:49,150
Oh! Oh!

42
00:01:49,234 --> 00:01:50,401
Joey, could I talk
to you for a second?

43
00:01:50,443 --> 00:01:51,569
Ooh! Oh-h-h!

44
00:01:51,611 --> 00:01:52,779
Joey, I need
to talk to you..

45
00:01:52,821 --> 00:01:55,281
Oh! Oh! Oh!

46
00:01:58,243 --> 00:01:59,953
Oh-h-h!

47
00:02:00,036 --> 00:02:01,538
[muffled screaming]

48
00:02:01,621 --> 00:02:03,248
No, no, no.

49
00:02:05,041 --> 00:02:06,084
Yes.

50
00:02:06,751 --> 00:02:08,211
Yes.

51
00:02:09,462 --> 00:02:11,756
You? And-and you?

52
00:02:13,174 --> 00:02:14,509
Yes, but you
cannot tell anyone.

53
00:02:14,592 --> 00:02:15,635
No one knows.

54
00:02:15,718 --> 00:02:17,887
How? When?

55
00:02:17,971 --> 00:02:20,557
- It happened in London.
- In London!

56
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:21,975
[indistinct shouting]

57
00:02:23,184 --> 00:02:24,602
The reason we
didn't tell anyone

58
00:02:24,644 --> 00:02:26,980
was 'cause we didn't want
to make a big deal out of it.

59
00:02:27,021 --> 00:02:29,816
But it is a big deal.

60
00:02:29,858 --> 00:02:32,735
- I have to tell someone!
- No, no, no.

61
00:02:32,819 --> 00:02:34,404
- You can't.
- Please, please.

62
00:02:34,487 --> 00:02:36,990
We just don't want to deal
with telling everyone, okay?

63
00:02:37,073 --> 00:02:39,200
Please, just promise
you won't tell.

64
00:02:43,163 --> 00:02:44,455
Alright.

65
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:48,668
Man, this is unbelievable.

66
00:02:48,751 --> 00:02:51,337
I mean, it's great. But..

67
00:02:52,797 --> 00:02:54,257
I know, it's great.

68
00:02:55,758 --> 00:02:57,886
Oh, I don't
want to see that.

69
00:03:01,347 --> 00:03:03,308
We're so stupid.

70
00:03:03,349 --> 00:03:05,602
Do you know what's
going on in there?

71
00:03:05,685 --> 00:03:07,812
They're trying
to take Joey.

72
00:03:09,981 --> 00:03:10,190
[instrumental music]

